The '''Endangered [[Shreebird]] Aviary''' was a wildlife refuge on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. During its grand opening in [[23 BBY/Legends|23 BBY]], Representative [[Jar Jar Binks/Legends|Jar Jar Binks]] deactivated the sky dome with disastrous consequences.<ref>{{HoloNetNewsWeb|45|news/13228_3.html|Rep. Binks Destroys Ice Statue at Gala Fundraiser}}</ref>

